Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going, Kazuki? You all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet. My books\Nhaven't been delivered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Doujin Queen,\Nthe great Eimi, has come to greet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Kazuki, I brought\Nyou some homemade cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo! Sendo!\NTake a look at my new costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, you're running late, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a man-made island off\Nthe beaten path on the edge of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is coming when this island\Nof cold concrete will be set ablaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People will gather, draw manga, search\Nfor manga, get passionate about manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A soulful festival of those who have\Nstaked their entire youths on doujinshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comic Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comic Party is now open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of a sudden,\Nyou took my hand in yours{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that we wouldn't\Nget separated in the crowd{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so happy I couldn't squeeze\Nyour hand very tightly in return{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day, I realized I was in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We started out as just friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now let's cross that boundary line{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And take off together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hold my feelings back\Nanymore It hurts so much I could cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, I can't lie to myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is embarrassing to ask, but{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please accept everything about me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, now and forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"I Want This Book to Sell!" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki! Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Subaru. How are things going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Subaru,\Ntake a look at Aya's book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an original hero story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's a hero story?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it will be my pleasure to read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! I'm so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the transformation\Nitem was the sunglasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's so cool that his\Nponytail turns into a blade too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so moved
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the effect of the gleaming background\Nwhen he revealed his true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru can't write a manga like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T... Two hundred yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Such a great book for only\Ntwo hundred yen? What a bargain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a fan of yours, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky I was able\Nto buy it before it sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's the only\Nbook we've sold all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it isn't just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People just don't seem to\Nbe interested in Aya's books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange! That's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a good book! Why doesn't it sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be someone's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A plot by some evil secret society!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only possible explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You're an evil villain aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Subaru, shall punish evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Subaru! He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you pick a fight with me,\NI have no choice but to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daiei Ryuu ultimate technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Subaru, you know better\Nthan to fight in the exhibition hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Aya here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru wants to get more\Ncustomers to read your books, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought the best thing would be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to get advice from popular\Nauthors who will be your teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu Inagawa is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu! When did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the small\Nstuff or you'll go bald early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited her from Kobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu's advice is worth listening to, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's helped me out a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in this industry, ya gotta help\Neach other out when you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing\Nyour doujinshi don't have:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's {\i1}passion{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning passion and\Nthe passion of infatuation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strength of your personal\Nfeelings toward the characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I mean by passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that into your pen, then let it\Nflow onto the blank manuscript paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passionate feelings will draw customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be passionate! Even if it whittles\Nyour life away, be passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that might be important too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next teacher has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am super pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great Eimi has come all the way here,\Nand you can't even come out to greet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down, would ya? Stupid Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done with my lecture yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the hot spring panda doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Did ya finish all\Nyour homework like you're supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure 'bout that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a teacher too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about me that way!\NYou're no big deal yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us some advice, Ms. Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the queen of the doujin world,\Nthe super-popular Eimi Ohba the great,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will give you a special election!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean "special lecture"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get a lecture from her,\Nher dumbness will rub off on ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just scoot on back to the\Nmountains of Kobe, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya think you're\Ndoin', ya big dummy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, hot spring panda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,---Panda! Panda! Panda! Panda! Panda!\N--Dummy! Dummy! Dummy! Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Panda! Panda! Panda! Panda!\N--Dummy! Dummy! Dummy! Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you two cut it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna fight, do it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I can't believe those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next teacher is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in trouble,\Nyoung man and young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I, Taishi Kuhonbutsu,\Nshow you how to catch an otaku's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of contraption\Ndid you make in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how long have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eternal brother,\NI am always by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stuff like that, it creeps me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so heartless, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:10:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we are going to cook this fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, mix this sticky liquid up really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But comrade! My lecture has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the fish is nice and brown,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's pour this liquid\Nover it nice and thick and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo! Sendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Reiko too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stand out, you need this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a plan to draw\Ncustomers to your space, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the plan's not too bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but who's going to wear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's try them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No peeking, Sendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a nicer figure than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might just have to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you guys get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sendo, which one\Ngot your blood pumping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point.\NLook, Aya looks embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya, if you don't want\Nto do this, just say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, don't worry so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're really\Nhappy deep down anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried making a new recipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look very good,\Nbut it smells kind of good,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think... it's... edible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulda seen this one coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need something to wipe it with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki? Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a horrible fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my manuscript got ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't redraw it soon,\NI won't make it by the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, rest until your fever breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you re-draw this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, does anything look strange about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've only done that one page.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll do the rest myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I keep resting,\NI won't make it by the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself. I'll do the rest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you do that. You\Nwon't finish your manuscript in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your health is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't publish your new book,\NSubaru will be so disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work on your own manuscript, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when your fever breaks,\Nhelp me with my manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please rest until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Send manuscript to printer!!"\N"Comipa"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Send manuscript to printer!!"\N"Comipa"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Send manuscript to printer!!"\N"Comipa"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Send manuscript to printer!!"\N"Comipa"{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thirty minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she didn't do very well today either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's seriously cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys, you can't just do\Nsomething like that without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious to see if Aya's book sold well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh... Uh huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cut it out, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen you two! You\Nshouldn't bother other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do that for all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am angry, young woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daiei Ryuu ultimate technique!\NDragon Fang Whirlwind Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice prevails!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Subaru, if you don't stop this right\Nnow, I'll be forced to ban you from the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that commotion's brought\Na lot of people around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at\NJamming Book Store's new issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Just a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at her book!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, may I take your picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I see one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is pretty good. I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.\NThat will be two hundred yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I take a look at one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comic Party is now closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hope to see you again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't sell many after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad that crowd\Ndidn't form just a little earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having my books read\Nby more people than usual
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Subaru,\NKazuki, and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope your books are read by\Neven more people at the next Comipa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki! Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your book sell well, Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work harder so you\Ncan sell even more the next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Subaru,\Nhow did your book sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't sell even one book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then next time it's Subaru's turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya, let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start living together right now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that's missing is time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think we need a place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where we can share our smiles,\Nour tears{\i0}, {\i1}and our free time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was with you,\NI could stay there forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know you don't\Nlike anything complicated{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I still keep on pulling your arms{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally found this 2LDK{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:22:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A table set would be fine too{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I think a kotatsu\Nwould be better after all{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time we spend\Njust lying around together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is more important than it sounds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not easy to find someone\Nyou can always accept{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And who will always accept you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you are that person for me, so{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start living together right now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that's missing is time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think we need a place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where we can share smiles,\Nour tears, and our free time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I was with you,\NI could stay there forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You want to go to the beach, don't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You want to go to the beach!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you talking about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like I said!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, all right!\NI want to go to the beach!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I guess there's\Nno choice. I'll go with you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow! I'm so happy! I get to\Ngo to the beach with the great Eimi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be grateful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But are you sure you'll be okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you sure you won't\Nhave summer classes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gulp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time: "Fumyuun!\NTake Me to the Beach!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to the beach!{\i0}
